John T. Rynd 
Executive Compensation
As Chief Executive Officer and President at HERCULES OFFSHORE INC, John T. Rynd  made $3,463,165 in total compensation.  Of this total $700,000 was received as a salary, $789,688 was received as a bonus, $0 was received in stock options, $680,760 was awarded as stock and $1,292,717 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2015 fiscal year. 


