Insider Activity


Individual




John T. Rynd



Mr. John T. Rynd is President & Chief Executive Officer at Hercules Offshore, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at Hornbeck Offshore Services, Inc. (Louisiana), Compressor Engineering Corp, Offshore Energy Center, The National Ocean Industries Association, TODCO and International Association of Drilling Contractors. Mr. Rynd was previously employed as President by Hercules Drilling Co. LLC, Vice President-Investor Relations by Noble Drilling Services, Inc., and Vice President-Marketing by Chiles Offshore Corp. He received his undergraduate degree from Texas A&M University.



